<div class="h-full flex flex-col">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-800 text-white border-b border-primary-700 shrink-0">
        <div class="h-14 flex items-center justify-between px-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                 <h1 class="font-bold flex items-center gap-2 text-lg">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-400">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 18" />
                    </svg>
                    Online Python Editor
                 </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span id="status-badge" class="text-xs text-white/80 font-medium w-20 text-right">Ready</span>
                <button id="run-btn" class="bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-300 text-slate-900 px-4 py-1.5 rounded text-sm font-bold transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span>Execute</span>
                     <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 5.653c0-1.426 1.529-2.33 2.779-1.643l11.54 6.348c1.295.712 1.295 2.573 0 3.285L7.28 19.991c-1.25.687-2.779-.217-2.779-1.643V5.653z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- SEO Text Section -->
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-1 text-sm text-primary-50 max-w-4xl opacity-90 leading-relaxed hidden md:block">
            <p>
                <strong>Online Python Editor</strong> modern dengan fitur syntax highlighting untuk pengalaman coding yang lebih baik. 
                Edit script Python Anda, lakukan debugging sederhana, dan lihat outputnya secara realtime. Solusi praktis bagi programmer Python yang ingin coding di mana saja tanpa ribet.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Split Area -->
    <div class="flex-1 flex min-h-0">
        <!-- Editor Column -->
        <div class="w-1/2 flex flex-col border-r border-slate-700">
             <div class="bg-[#1e293b] flex-1 relative overflow-auto">
                <pre class="h-full language-python"><code id="editor" class="language-python focus:outline-none p-4 block min-h-full" contenteditable="true" spellcheck="false"># Python Editor Online
# Mulai koding disini...

import random

numbers = [random.randint(1, 100) for _ in range(10)]
print(f"Random numbers: {numbers}")
print(f"Sorted: {sorted(numbers)}")
</code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Output Column -->
        <div class="w-1/2 flex flex-col bg-slate-950">
            <div class="flex-1 p-4 font-mono text-sm text-blue-200 overflow-auto whitespace-pre-wrap" id="output">
                // Output will appear here...
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

